net.sourceforge.jaad.aac

Enum Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Profile>
      • net.sourceforge.jaad.aac.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Profile>

    public enum Profile
extends java.lang.Enum<Profile>
    Different AAC profiles. The function Decoder.canDecode specifies if the decoder can handle a given format. More precisely, the ISO standard calls these 'object types'.

      • isErrorResilientProfile

        public boolean isErrorResilientProfile()
        Returns a boolean, indicating if this profile contains error resilient tools. That is, if it's index is higher than 16, since the first error resilient profile is ER_AAC_LC (17). This method is mainly used internally.
        Returns:
        true if the profile uses error resilience
